    <item>
      <title>特斯拉说，这可能面临贸易战争的报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-14/tesla-says-it-could-face-retaliation-for-trade-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司（Tesla Inc.）表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统采取的举动将关税纳入广泛进口的行动之后，贸易战升级，对其他国家的潜在报复性举动表示关注。彭博的克雷格·特鲁德尔（Craig Trudell）报告了“彭博监视”。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-14/tesla-says-it-could-face-retaliation-for-trade-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 14:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的埃斯克里瓦（Escriva）认为基线场景的风险“非常重要”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/ecb-s-escriva-sees-very-significant-risks-to-baseline-scenario</link>
      <description><![CDATA[理事会成员何塞·路易斯·埃斯克里瓦（Jose Luis Escriva）表示，欧洲中央银行对通货膨胀和经济增长的假设在每个方向上都面临着巨大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/ecb-s-escriva-sees-very-significant-risks-to-baseline-scenario</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国机构警告不要结束对化石燃料加热的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/german-agency-warns-against-ending-ban-on-fossil-fuel-heating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国环境局警告即将上任的政府不要抛弃对化石燃料供暖系统的禁令，该国准备险些错过其在住房和运输部门的2030年气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/german-agency-warns-against-ending-ban-on-fossil-fuel-heating</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核电繁荣意味着即使德国也正在汲取新的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/nuclear-power-boom-means-even-germany-is-drawing-new-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对原子力量的复兴兴趣意味着，即使在德国，世界第二大提供商的富集铀也在扩大，尽管在德国中，这仍然是国际燃料周期中的重要联系，尽管关闭了所有反应堆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/nuclear-power-boom-means-even-germany-is-drawing-new-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:23:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从关税触发的更正中，美国股票面临不平衡的恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/us-stocks-face-uneven-recovery-from-tariff-triggered-correction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票只花了16次交易，就可以进行更正，使一条疲惫的华尔街询问白宫官员警告的“调整期”要持续了多长时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/us-stocks-face-uneven-recovery-from-tariff-triggered-correction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:07:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国债券抛售重新点燃，因为梅尔斯罢工债务交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/german-bond-selloff-reignites-with-debt-package-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总理当选弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）以债务资助的国防和基础设施支出方案赢得了政治支持之后，德国债券的抛售在周五获得了关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/german-bond-selloff-reignites-with-debt-package-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚动荡延迟预算修复使投资者处于边缘状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/romanian-turmoil-delaying-budget-fix-puts-bond-investors-on-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚动荡的政治使投资者保持警惕，即提高欧盟最风险的政府债券所需的进一步的财政步骤将面临进一步的延误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/romanian-turmoil-delaying-budget-fix-puts-bond-investors-on-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 09:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坦克供应商史蒂尔（Steyr）甚至以541％的拉力赛将莱茵金属（Rheinmentall）黯然失色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/europe-s-top-returning-stock-still-has-10-year-demand-boom-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯蒂尔汽车公司（Steyr Motors AG）是奥地利用于坦克和军船的柴油发动机制造商，他说，在今年将其股票提高了540％以上的军备竞赛中，它很容易达到欧洲需求，以满足欧洲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/europe-s-top-returning-stock-still-has-10-year-demand-boom-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 07:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗，阿波罗测试私人信用搭档在波音单位销售中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/citi-apollo-test-new-private-credit-tie-up-in-boeing-unit-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，花旗集团和阿波罗全球管理公司（Apollo Global Management Inc.）为波音公司的耶普森导航部门提供潜在的买家，可以选择通过这对夫妇的新生私人信贷合作伙伴关系为收购提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/citi-apollo-test-new-private-credit-tie-up-in-boeing-unit-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 00:48:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票在令人惊叹的华尔街周末攀登：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票的反弹使股票投资者平静下来，但唐纳德·特朗普的政治动作的后果继续震撼全球市场。随着政府领导人同意大规模的国防支出方案，德国债券的收益率激增，而最终的避风港资产也是如此。黄金＆mdash;首次超过3,000美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:34:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
